    public abstract class EntityHandle
extends com.bergerkiller.mountiplex.reflection.declarations.Template.Handle
    Instance wrapper handle for type net.minecraft.server.Entity. To access members without creating a handle type, use the static T member. New handles can be created from raw instances using createHandle(Object).
